data.description: Well maintained home close to Stone Lake beach and park. Home is perched nicely up on a hill on a corner lot. The home has 3 bedrooms, 1 full bath and 2 half baths. Kitchen and main bath have been updated. There are 2 natural gas fireplaces, one in the main living room and one in the basement. Basement can be finished for more living space. Above the garage is an extra living area. It has been used for related living or can be another bedroom. Possibilities are endless. Large back yard with 2 sheds for storage. Newer Furnace, A/C, hot water heater and dishwasher. Spend your summer down at the beach or yachting on Stone Lake.
